{"id": "ChIJBa5WNwDDwoARsscPO5mCFYk", "rating": 4.4, "userRatingCount": 261, "displayName": {"text": "BadAshBakes", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJBa5WNwDDwoARsscPO5mCFYk/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2taSE1EUjJNVEpyVjFBM09IZDNTSGsxTTNndGQxRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "4 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "My sister and I went on Valentine’s Day, and everything was a 10/10. The line was out the door and took about 25 minutes, but it was well worth the wait in my opinion.\n\nThe matcha blondie had a strong matcha flavor, which I loved, and it wasn’t too sweet. The banana pudding was even better the next day after sitting in the fridge, and the red velvet cinnamon roll—OMG.\n\nOh, and the banana strawberry matcha was so good as well. I definitely recommend giving it a try!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "My sister and I went on Valentine’s Day, and everything was a 10/10. The line was out the door and took about 25 minutes, but it was well worth the wait in my opinion.\n\nThe matcha blondie had a strong matcha flavor, which I loved, and it wasn’t too sweet. The banana pudding was even better the next day after sitting in the fridge, and the red velvet cinnamon roll—OMG.\n\nOh, and the banana strawberry matcha was so good as well. I definitely recommend giving it a try!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Shaela Reeves", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/108763530968309111620/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUNQiaIIwihg_PuVfLAcD_8_iUQyU-RwM1mHHek9PTmiCK3Y_o28w=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba2"}, "publishTime": "2026-02-15T23:05:34.457568903Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2taSE1EUjJNVEpyVjFBM09IZDNTSGsxTTNndGQxRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2taSE1EUjJNVEpyVjFBM09IZDNTSGsxTTNndGQxRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c3003756ae05:0x891582993b0fc7b2"}, {"name": "places/ChIJBa5WNwDDwoARsscPO5mCFYk/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21kMGJtWmxaRE5qWmxSNlZVdDVkWFU1TnpKeFNFRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "Visited here to try matcha cinnamon roll!\nVery curious about this matcha cinnamon roll bc i just never thought about bringing matcha to cinnamon roll.\nMy overall impression of matcha cinnamon roll was underwhelming. Maybe I had a bit too much expectation. It felt a bit too wet to me; couldnt tell if cinnamon and matcha were getting along for me.\nBeside matcha cinnamon roll, I tried s’more cookie and that was GREAT!\nLoved chewiness and perfect level of sweetness of their cookies!!\nWhen I visit next time, im thinking of trying regular cinnamon roll and diff sweets/pastries.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Visited here to try matcha cinnamon roll!\nVery curious about this matcha cinnamon roll bc i just never thought about bringing matcha to cinnamon roll.\nMy overall impression of matcha cinnamon roll was underwhelming. Maybe I had a bit too much expectation. It felt a bit too wet to me; couldnt tell if cinnamon and matcha were getting along for me.\nBeside matcha cinnamon roll, I tried s’more cookie and that was GREAT!\nLoved chewiness and perfect level of sweetness of their cookies!!\nWhen I visit next time, im thinking of trying regular cinnamon roll and diff sweets/pastries.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Denny", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/111503132443061485538/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV24jhgEPGifB8h_iyJkHRM-5VXuarTiOeLgbO3XD6WXNxIt4Y=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-11T04:31:20.134407501Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21kMGJtWmxaRE5qWmxSNlZVdDVkWFU1TnpKeFNFRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21kMGJtWmxaRE5qWmxSNlZVdDVkWFU1TnpKeFNFRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c3003756ae05:0x891582993b0fc7b2"}, {"name": "places/ChIJBa5WNwDDwoARsscPO5mCFYk/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25OU2NEazJWRVZoTTNOSlJGQTNUVkEyUXpOMlZFRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "4 months ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "Looking for a sweet treat to share with your loved ones this Valentine's Day? Look no further than this amazing bakery my sister and I visited! We tried the Red Velvet Cinnamon Roll, Classic Cinnamon, Coffee Cake, Toffee Chocolate Chip Cookies, Cornbread Cookies and White Chocolate Macadamia. And let me tell you, they were all absolutely delicious!\n\nMy personal favorite has always been the Classic Cinnamon rolls. They're so moist and flavorful, even days later! The red velvet cinnamon rolls were a close second though. The coffee cake was perfect, the cookies were to die for, and our Hot Americano was served fresh and hot.\n\nThe only downside was the long wait - we stood in line for an hour on Valentine's Day! But the friendly staff and amazing treats made it worth it. Just make sure to plan ahead for parking, as they don't have a lot. Overall, a great experience and I highly recommend checking them out for yourself! #SweetTreats #ValentinesDayDelight 😋🧁☕️", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Looking for a sweet treat to share with your loved ones this Valentine's Day? Look no further than this amazing bakery my sister and I visited! We tried the Red Velvet Cinnamon Roll, Classic Cinnamon, Coffee Cake, Toffee Chocolate Chip Cookies, Cornbread Cookies and White Chocolate Macadamia. And let me tell you, they were all absolutely delicious!\n\nMy personal favorite has always been the Classic Cinnamon rolls. They're so moist and flavorful, even days later! The red velvet cinnamon rolls were a close second though. The coffee cake was perfect, the cookies were to die for, and our Hot Americano was served fresh and hot.\n\nThe only downside was the long wait - we stood in line for an hour on Valentine's Day! But the friendly staff and amazing treats made it worth it. Just make sure to plan ahead for parking, as they don't have a lot. Overall, a great experience and I highly recommend checking them out for yourself! #SweetTreats #ValentinesDayDelight 😋🧁☕️", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Marie Edwards", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/105886979203593599574/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWbKRBr9mRjvXHwfDdhXBFGbH526QXBu-zHzHsmNHVsBxbT3pya=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6"}, "publishTime": "2026-02-16T20:22:24.005720711Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25OU2NEazJWRVZoTTNOSlJGQTNUVkEyUXpOMlZFRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25OU2NEazJWRVZoTTNOSlJGQTNUVkEyUXpOMlZFRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c3003756ae05:0x891582993b0fc7b2"}, {"name": "places/ChIJBa5WNwDDwoARsscPO5mCFYk/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21wclJtRnpkQzF2ZEZJeE4wZEVNSGRuUVhwR1lWRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Great service and great food.\nLOVED the banana bread most!\nToffee chocolate chip cookie was also a favorite.\nI'm not a matcha person but had to try the matcha cinnamon roll and it was actually very good. We also loved the regular cinnamon roll too.\nHonestly everything was great, stop by if in Pasadena area.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Great service and great food.\nLOVED the banana bread most!\nToffee chocolate chip cookie was also a favorite.\nI'm not a matcha person but had to try the matcha cinnamon roll and it was actually very good. We also loved the regular cinnamon roll too.\nHonestly everything was great, stop by if in Pasadena area.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Katy Brown", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/110588223104948029876/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWKB2TrTuSed9H75tIcWStknZcBhMBBv_-Xs7075RmIioOb88T_=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-03T23:17:55.643024237Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21wclJtRnpkQzF2ZEZJeE4wZEVNSGRuUVhwR1lWRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21wclJtRnpkQzF2ZEZJeE4wZEVNSGRuUVhwR1lWRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c3003756ae05:0x891582993b0fc7b2"}, {"name": "places/ChIJBa5WNwDDwoARsscPO5mCFYk/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tkc05YQjFjWEpuV0ZoS2JtMURkVzVTWm1GWE4wRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "7 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Always a pleasant experience coming to support a beautiful Black woman owned business in Pasadena. You can see Ashley’s passion in every corner of this space, especially as her lovely mother breezes from kitchen to display counter to fill baby missing items. The matcha is top notch quality, fun latte flavors and seasonal offerings. Definitely a must when in Dena.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Always a pleasant experience coming to support a beautiful Black woman owned business in Pasadena. You can see Ashley’s passion in every corner of this space, especially as her lovely mother breezes from kitchen to display counter to fill baby missing items. The matcha is top notch quality, fun latte flavors and seasonal offerings. Definitely a must when in Dena.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "breana jackson", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/108280431938650576852/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXGDlJtCvpeIH29WNPlVCyx2escNqfRMKcGFjmwK4YlpiAMUDqp=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2025-12-13T20:18:09.066614860Z", "flagContentUri": "http